refer my tax dollars to go toward decriminalization and drug treatment than to just have cops shoot them, or throw them in jail. The fewer people going to prison, the more workers you would have access to, as businesses tend to shy away from ex-cons. (Even if they say they don't, and that you have an equal chance of getting the job.)

I would love to have my tax dollars go toward REAL affordable housing, not just warming centers and places that lock their doors if you aren't in by a certain time. Imagine taking just one old hotel and turning it into an apartment complex for the homeless in your city. They all would have a lockable room, their own bathroom, access to a workout room, a pool, maybe even keep the continental breakfast going. That would be fantastic.

Obviously the universal healthcare would be a benefit for everyone, even me. What I'd like to see is cheaper fucking dental work. I was big into Mountain Dew, and five crowns later I'm still working to repair the damage. But there are people even worse off than me in that department, so my tax dollars could help them as well.

There's just so much that could be done better by people that aren't carrying a gun, and might confuse their taser with it. Police shouldn't have need for military grade riot gear, that's what the National Guard should be for.

I know, some of these ideas might be too progressive for you right now, and it's okay to feel scared about change, that's natural. But there are people out there that desperately need things to change. Us waiting, twiddling our thumbs, is causing deaths. People avoiding hospitals for critical ailments, people unable to afford masks and catching/spreading Covid, people unable to get access to birth control and having kids they didn't plan for. Talk to your younger family, see what they think about these issues, and above all, don't hate them for having different opinions than you. I'm pretty sure my grandparents would disown us if they found out we are pro-choice. A cousin was afraid to come out to them because they might get disowned for being gay. They're afraid what you will think of them, what you'll say to them, that you might never want to see them again. We need to be able to talk openly, share ideas, viewpoints. 

We need to help each other understand.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Vm54YZ0</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Onlyhereforthelaughs]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>ghost it notes</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/UFIBNMm</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NNTzKCd.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/UFIBNMm</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[zoraniko]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>The salon</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/d6cAX26</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/oCo1oB8.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/d6cAX26</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mmmmaybenot]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>random cdn</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/VXFDX7n</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7Cr4tiN.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nrypLt1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/yc4heKw.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QIawarS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/mC6SLaf.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cvKxShw.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/VXFDX7n</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[cdnanon]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Hello There</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/lA7aSpE</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nQhQOqn.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div